content.html: Oh sweetie, too much. I’m a mum & though I’m sure you have good intentions it’s never a good look to slut-shame women. Massive patriarchal overtones to your comment, which you may not see, but one day you’ll realise how unfair it is to condemn women for a healthy natural impulse.
